To provide for the following Heads of Departments in the Forest Department other than the appointing authority:
It was under the consideration of the government.
The Government's Decisions:

Under the provisions of Rule 4 (1) of the Maharashtra Civil Services (Discipline and Appeal) Rules, 1979, there is a provision for suspension of Group-A and Group-B (Gazetted) officers of the Forest Department. Apart from the appointing authority, the powers of the governor are vested in the following heads of departments of the forest department.
